OL,3,CWhen will snow hit the UK and how long
OL,4,Cwill it last?
OL,6,FAmber weather warnings for snow have
OL,7,Fcome into force for parts of northern
OL,8,FEngland and Wales. Thousands of people
OL,9,Fhave been warned of travel disruption
OL,11,Fforecasters have issued warnings for
OL,12,FThursday with widespread snow and rain
OL,13,Fforecast across large parts of the
OL,14,Fcountry.
OL,16,FAmber weather warnings for snow have
OL,17,Fbeen issued for parts of northern
OL,18,FEngland and North Wales, while a
OL,19,Fmixture of yellow rain and snow
OL,20,Fwarnings will be in force across the
OL,21,Ffour nations.
