OL,3,CWhen will snow hit the UK and how long
OL,4,Cwill it last?
OL,6,FHow long is the snow forecasted for?
OL,8,FA cold, frosty and, for some, icy
OL,9,Fnight ahead.
OL,11,FWe've got rain moving into southern
OL,12,FBritain later tonight and moving
OL,13,Fgradually northwards through Thursday.
OL,15,FMany areas of England and Wales will
OL,16,Fhave a very wet start with several
OL,17,Fhours of steady rathe rain, that will
OL,18,Fclash with cold air and turn to a
OL,19,Fwintry mix of freezing rain, sleet and
OL,20,Fsnow - mostly across Wales, northern
OL,21,FEngland and the Midlands.
