OL,3,CWhen will snow hit the UK and how long
OL,4,Cwill it last?
OL,6,FThis cold snap is relatively short
OL,7,Flived as gradually we'll see less cold
OL,8,F- for many milder - air return later
OL,9,Fin the week.
OL,11,FWhat are the areas most impacted?
OL,13,FThe areas most impacted by snow will
OL,14,Fbe higher ground of northern England,
OL,15,Fthe Midlands and Wales.
OL,17,FMost notably mountains of north Wales
OL,18,Fand parts of the Pennines, where amber
OL,19,Fweather warnings remain in place. The
OL,20,Feast facing slopes of these areas will
OL,21,Fsee the most snow.
