OL,3,CWhen will snow hit the UK and how long
OL,4,Cwill it last?
OL,6,FAcross higher routes the brisk
OL,7,Feasterly winds will mean blowing snow
OL,8,Fbringing a risk of challenging,
OL,9,Fdisruptive travel for a time.
OL,11,FThe snow will turn readily to sleet
OL,12,Fand rain by the end of Thursday
OL,13,Fafternoon for these areas.
OL,15,FDo we know when it will become warmer
OL,16,Fagain?
OL,18,FI wouldn't use the term "warm" this
OL,19,Ftime of year but less cold or
OL,20,Frelatively milder air returns later in
OL,21,Fthe week and any snow will melt.
