OL,3,CWhen will snow hit the UK and how long
OL,4,Cwill it last?
OL,6,FAs temperatures recover and with more
OL,7,Frain forecast to move from south to
OL,8,Fnorth, there will be more standing
OL,9,Fwater.
OL,11,FTogether, with saturated ground, this
OL,12,Fwill bring the risk of flooding in the
OL,13,Fmost prone areas, particularly across
OL,14,Fsouthern Britain.
